              <span id="reviewTextContainer2885354654" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3036424820988243774"><strong>Good finish for the series </strong><br/><br/>I did enjoy this book but the first one was the best in the series. I missed some of the original characters but the new ones were pretty good replacements. The story ends nicely with no loose ends I can think of. Good amount if action and suspense. If you are a fan of the first two, you should read this one, you won&apos;t regret it.</span>
  <span id="freeText3036424820988243774" style="display:none"><strong>Good finish for the series </strong><br /><br />I did enjoy this book but the first one was the best in the series. I missed some of the original characters but the new ones were pretty good replacements. The story ends nicely with no loose ends I can think of. Good amount if action and suspense. If you are a fan of the first two, you should read this one, you won't regret it.</span>
