<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3605324-contagious"><img alt="Contagious (Infected, #2)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388273040l/3605324._SX50_.jpg" />
